1
00:00:58,890 --> 00:01:02,890
Little White Snake, even though you have taken human form,

2
00:01:03,049 --> 00:01:07,290
[Xue Linglong, Thousand-year-old Snake Fairy] You must find
your destined bond before you can ascend to immortality.

3
00:01:51,570 --> 00:01:52,449
Sister.

4
00:01:55,850 --> 00:01:56,809
Are you Qingdai?

5
00:02:02,050 --> 00:02:03,130
You're being naughty again.

6
00:02:03,410 --> 00:02:06,249
You're a woman, why did you transform into a man?

7
00:02:08,970 --> 00:02:11,729
When I was wandering, I once
passed by the shore of the merfolk.

8
00:02:12,449 --> 00:02:15,449
There, I met a handsome young man.

9
00:02:17,130 --> 00:02:20,329
I transformed into his appearance. Sister do you like it?

10
00:02:22,850 --> 00:02:23,489
Qingdai.

11
00:02:25,570 --> 00:02:29,130
I can't waste any more time with you on this mountain.

12
00:02:32,489 --> 00:02:36,090
You and I practice together. How is that wasting time?

13
00:02:39,570 --> 00:02:46,169
Qingdai, I have failed to successfully ascend in
past tribulations, all because of this unresolved bond.

14
00:02:48,609 --> 00:02:50,049
You continue to practice well here.

15
00:02:50,810 --> 00:02:53,850
Wait for me to resolve this bond and come back to you.

16
00:02:58,250 --> 00:03:02,329
But where do you find your bond?

17
00:03:05,690 --> 00:03:11,250
As the matchmaking god has clearly shown,
it's in the depths of Lin'an Bamboo Forest.

18
00:03:15,970 --> 00:03:17,570
Sister, you are really heartless.

19
00:03:38,547 --> 00:03:40,304
[Lin Haoxuan, Charming Demon Catcher]

20
00:04:17,649 --> 00:04:18,570
Demon-Slaying Sword, 12th form.

21
00:04:29,130 --> 00:04:30,209
Where do you think you're running, demon?

22
00:04:30,649 --> 00:04:32,570
Who told you that all beautiful women are demons?

23
00:04:33,570 --> 00:04:34,649
My master did.

24
00:04:35,690 --> 00:04:36,810
Demon-Slaying Sword, 16th form.

25
00:05:13,769 --> 00:05:17,130
Why do I have a good feeling
about him while he tries to catch me?

26
00:05:24,209 --> 00:05:27,610
Young master, are you saving me or capturing me?

27
00:05:35,610 --> 00:05:39,329
Didn't your master tell you?
A gentleman desires a virtuous lady.

28
00:05:39,329 --> 00:05:42,089
I am a cultivator, not a demon.

29
00:05:46,089 --> 00:05:47,130
I was being presumptuous.

30
00:05:51,449 --> 00:05:52,490
I am Lin Haoxuan.

31
00:05:52,930 --> 00:05:56,329
If my lady doesn't mind, please come and visit my house.

32
00:05:57,130 --> 00:05:58,250
Visit your house?

33
00:05:59,010 --> 00:05:59,889
Alright.

34
00:06:07,289 --> 00:06:11,529
My ancestors have been living in the mountains
for generations, skilled in the art of illusion.

35
00:06:12,649 --> 00:06:14,449
I was going to Lin'an Bamboo Forest to search for someone.

36
00:06:14,690 --> 00:06:17,969
I didn't expect you to mistake me for a demon.

37
00:06:18,209 --> 00:06:19,170
Please don't blame yourself.

38
00:06:19,810 --> 00:06:21,849
I am the one who should be blamed.

39
00:06:30,449 --> 00:06:32,050
It only moves when it detects demonic energy.

40
00:07:08,969 --> 00:07:12,730
You deceitful demon, show your true form!

41
00:08:02,289 --> 00:08:03,969
What a naive demon hunter!

42
00:08:04,370 --> 00:08:08,769
You think a demon-subduing tune can defeat me?
I haven't cultivated for a thousand years in vain.

43
00:08:35,970 --> 00:08:37,809
She should have been in pain and revealed her true form.

44
00:08:44,090 --> 00:08:45,490
I don't believe I can't catch you.
